ent-AU14WeaponSMGXMP5A6HAZOPS = XMP5A6/10 CQW
    .desc = Winner of the 2172 HAZOPS Close Quarters Weapon program, this German-based "SMG" answers the question; "What if we put the standard USCMC rifle caliber in a machinepistol?". Despite low accuracy, it has a high firerate and impressive stopping power. Chambered in 10x24mm. Can load M41A magazines.
ent-AU14AttachmentM203A4GrenadeLauncher = M203A4 grenade launcher
    .desc = A weapon-mounted, reloadable grenade launcher.
ent-AU14MagazineXMP5A6 = XMP5A6 magazine (10x24mm)
    .desc = What have they done with my bannana clip? Uses 10x24mm.
